channel.title: Working 614 Client
channel.description:
Hi i am releasing a 614 Working client that wont stop at 0% and stuff like that. If you get this [img]http://i38.tinypic.com/2qwkl85.jpg[/img]
go to your client folder>>open "Class47" and Find "String[] strings_3"
you should find [code] String[] strings_3_ = {"cache614", ".file_store_" + i_2_};[/code]
Replace that with this [code]String[] strings_3_ = {".jagex_cache_" + i_2_, ".file_store_" + i_2_};[/code]
Save,Compile.
Next, download cache and extract it to your c:/ Cache http://www.mediafire.com/?71d15s4724k11xa
Now download the 614 Client. Client http://www.mediafire.com/?m79xgja6xr5pt7h
This is already at 127.0.0.1 if you want to change go to launch.java client.java applet_sub1.java
and change all teh 127.0.0.1 to your ip.
